title: Margot Robbie and Allison Janney going for the 'EGOT' on the UK red carpet
text:
Margot Robbie and Allison Janney going for the 'EGOT' on the UK red carpet Friday, February 16, 2018 - 01:34 
Oscar and BAFTA nominee Janney says she and fellow nominee Robbie are going for figure skating's acting equivalent of the triple axel, the 'EGOT'. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
